What, a level so big that it counts as two exits? ...Wait, that actually makes sense, because you're gonna have me hit switch palace switches within each of those four doors up there, which will all count as normal exits, and then they'll fill in the bridge down here, which'll lead to the secret exit, right?

And that would be the secret exit to Switch Room, as expected. This reveals The Space Hideout, which I'll be playing next time!
